<http://www.semanticweb.org/joann/ontologies/2026/2/eudamed-ontology/ClassI> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A low‑risk medical device under MDR 2017/745, typically subject to self‑declaration of conformity."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/joann/ontologies/2026/2/eudamed-ontology/ClassI> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Class I medical device"@en .
# 
