<http://www.semanticweb.org/joann/ontologies/2026/2/eudamed-ontology/ClassIII> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://schema.org/MedicalDevice> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/joann/ontologies/2026/2/eudamed-ontology/ClassIII> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A high‑risk medical device under MDR 2017/745, requiring the highest level of scrutiny and clinical evaluation."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/joann/ontologies/2026/2/eudamed-ontology/ClassIII> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Class III medical device"@en .
