<http://www.semanticweb.org/joann/ontologies/2026/2/eudamed-ontology/ClassIIb> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A medium‑high risk medical device under MDR 2017/745, subject to strict conformity assessment procedures."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/joann/ontologies/2026/2/eudamed-ontology/ClassIIb> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Class IIb medical device"@en .
